---

<BaseLayout
  title="Blog"
  description={"Nice Blog Posts and Articles that Increase Your Knowladge in Web Development."}
>
  <div class="w-full grow bg-[#12181b]">
    <div class="pt-16 pb-5 text-gray-600 body-font lg:pb-auto lg:pt-20">
      <div
        class="container flex flex-col items-start justify-center px-5 mx-auto"
      >
        <div class="mx-auto lg:w-4/6">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-20 sm:flex-row sm:gap-10">
            <div
              class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start text-center sm:w-1/3 sm:py-8 shrink-0"
            >
              <div
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 bg-gray-200 rounded-full shrink-0"
              >
                <img
                  src={personalImage}
                  alt="My Personal Photo"
                  class="border-4 border-orange-500 rounded-full dark:border-white w-40 h-40 shrink-0"
                />
              </div>
              <div
                class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center"
              >
                <h2
                  class="mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-orange-500 title-font dark:text-white"
                >
                  Ahmed Mohamed
                </h2>
                <div class="w-12 h-1 mt-2 mb-4 bg-orange-500 rounded"></div>
                <p class="text-base text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                  Hello there, I am Ahmed Mohamed, I am FullStack Web Developer.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 pt-5 text-xl social-icons"
              >
                <a
                  href="https://www.facebook.com/a7m3dmohmd/"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="p-2 duration-500 bg-gray-700/70 rounded-xl hover:bg-[#097eeb] shrink-0"
                >
                  <img class="w-6 h-6" src={facebookIcon} alt="" srcset="" />
                </a>
                <a
                  href="https://twitter.com/a7m3D_000"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="p-2 duration-500 bg-gray-700/70 rounded-xl hover:bg-[#1d9bf0] shrink-0"
                >
                  <img
                    class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0"
                    src={githubIcon}
                    alt=""
                    srcset=""
                  />
                </a>
                <a
                  href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ahmedmohmd/"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="p-2 duration-500 bg-gray-700/70 rounded-xl hover:bg-[#0a66c2] shrink-0"
                >
                  <img
                    class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0"
                    src={linkedinIcon}
                    alt=""
                    srcset=""
                  />
                </a>
                <a
                  href="https://github.com/ahmedmohmd"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="p-2 duration-500 bg-gray-700/70 rounded-xl hover:bg-[#161b22] shrink-0"
                >
                  <img
                    class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0"
                    src={githubIcon}
                    alt=""
                    srcset=""
                  />
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap flex-col pb-24 mx-auto">
              <div class="relative flex pt-10 pb-20 sm:items-center">
                <div
                  class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full"
                >
                  <div class="w-1 h-full bg-gray-200 pointer-events-none"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-10 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-orange-500 rounded-full sm:mt-0 title-font"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-start flex-grow pl-6 md:pl-8 sm:items-center sm:flex-row"
                >
                  <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 text-orange-500 bg-orange-100 rounded-full"
                  >
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      class="w-10 h-10"
                      fill="none"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      stroke-width={2}
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                      ></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="flex flex-col flex-grow gap-2 mt-6 sm:pl-6 sm:mt-0"
                  >
                    <h2
                      class="mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-orange-500 title-font dark:text-white"
                    >
                      What I do?
                    </h2>
                    <p
                      class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >
                      I am a FullStack Developer, Who Work in Two Parts of
                      Making Website Process.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-1 bt-6">
                      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                        <svg
                          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                          class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500"
                          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                          fill="currentColor"
                        >
                          <path
                            fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <h3
                          class="font-semibold text-orange-500 dark:text-white"
                        >
                          Front End
                        </h3>
                      </div>
                      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1">
                        <svg
                          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                          class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500"
                          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                          fill="currentColor"
                        >
                          <path
                            fill-rule="evenodd"
                            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <h3
                          class="font-semibold text-orange-500 dark:text-white"
                        >
                          Back End
                        </h3>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative flex w-full pb-20 sm:items-center">
                <div
                  class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full"
                >
                  <div class="w-1 h-full bg-gray-200 pointer-events-none"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center self-start justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-10 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-orange-500 rounded-full sm:mt-9 title-font"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-start flex-grow pl-6 md:pl-8 sm:flex-row"
                >
                  <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 text-orange-500 bg-orange-100 rounded-full"
                  >
                    <img src={skillsIcon} alt="" class="w-14 h-14" />
                  </div>
                  <div
                    class="flex flex-col flex-grow gap-2 mt-6 sm:pl-6 sm:mt-0"
                  >
                    <h2
                      class="mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-orange-500 title-font dark:text-white"
                    >
                      Skills
                    </h2>
                    <p
                      class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >
                      My Skills in Frontend and Backend.
                    </p>
                    <div
                      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between w-full gap-1 bt-6"
                    >
                      {
                        mySkills.map(({ skillName, progress, width }) => {
                          return (
                            <ProgressBar
                              skillName={skillName}
                              progress={progress}
                              width={width}
                            />
                          );
                        })
                      }
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative flex pb-20 sm:items-center">
                <div
                  class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full"
                >
                  <div class="w-1 h-full bg-gray-200 pointer-events-none"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-10 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-orange-500 rounded-full sm:mt-0 title-font"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-start flex-grow pl-6 md:pl-8 sm:items-center sm:flex-row"
                >
                  <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 text-orange-500 bg-orange-100 rounded-full"
                  >
                    <img
                      src={educationIcon}
                      alt="Education"
                      class="w-14 h-14"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-grow mt-6 sm:pl-6 sm:mt-0">
                    <h2
                      class="mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-orange-500 title-font dark:text-white"
                    >
                      Education
                    </h2>
                    <p
                      class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >
                      Electrical Power Engineering Student at SVU.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative flex pb-20 sm:items-center">
                <div
                  class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full"
                >
                  <div class="w-1 h-full bg-gray-200 pointer-events-none"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-10 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-orange-500 rounded-full sm:mt-0 title-font"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-start flex-grow pl-6 md:pl-8 sm:items-center sm:flex-row"
                >
                  <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 text-orange-500 bg-orange-100 rounded-full"
                  >
                    <img src={hoppiesIcon} alt="" class="w-14 h-14" />
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-grow mt-6 sm:pl-6 sm:mt-0">
                    <h2
                      class="mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-orange-500 title-font dark:text-white"
                    >
                      Hoppies
                    </h2>
                    <p
                      class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >
                      I love shearing Knowladge with Aothers and Learn New
                      Things Every Day. <br />I love Reading and Writing.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative flex pb-20 sm:items-center">
                <div
                  class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-full"
                >
                  <div class="w-1 h-full bg-gray-200 pointer-events-none"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="relative z-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 mt-10 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-orange-500 rounded-full sm:mt-0 title-font"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                  class="flex flex-col items-start flex-grow pl-6 md:pl-8 sm:items-center sm:flex-row"
                >
                  <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-24 h-24 text-orange-500 bg-orange-100 rounded-full"
                  >
                    <img src={experienceIcon} alt="" class="w-14 h-14" />
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-grow mt-6 sm:pl-6 sm:mt-0">
                    <h2
                      class="mb-1 text-xl font-semibold text-orange-500 title-font dark:text-white"
                    >
                      Experience
                    </h2>
                    <p
                      class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
                    >
                      I am Student Now, I hope to be Professional Programmer in
                      The Future.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
